To build this package, you should be using an Ubuntu, Debian or similar system. Navigate to the parent folder and issue the command:

	dpkg-deb -b ./apple-icloud-online/ 

This should yeild an installable package called "apple-icloud-online.deb". You can then install this package with the command 

	dpkg -i ./apple-icloud-online.deb

This will add a menu to your application menu under LXDE, Gnome, etc that gives you direct launchers for the various applications in this suite. 
